Privacy Policy
Effective Date: June 22, 2024
Introduction
​
Little Love (“we,” “us,” or “our”) respects the privacy of our users (“you” or “your”). This Privacy Policy describes the types of information we collect through our mobile application, Little Love (“App”), how we use that information, and your choices regarding your information.
​
Information We Collect
We collect two types of information through the App:
Personally Identifiable Information (PII): This may include information that can be used to identify you directly, such as:
Name
Email address
Phone number (optional)
Username (if applicable)
Usage Data: This information is collected automatically when you use the App and does not identify you directly. It may include:
Device type and operating system
Usage statistics within the App
IP address (may be collected but not used to identify you)
Crash logs and other diagnostic data
How We Collect Information
We collect information directly from you when you provide it to us, such as when you create an account (if applicable). We also collect information automatically through the App using cookies or similar technologies.
Cookies and Similar Technologies
We may use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your experience with the App. Cookies are small files stored on your device that remember information about your activity on the App. You can choose to disable cookies through your device settings. However, this may limit your ability to use certain features of the App.
How We Use Your Information
We use the information we collect for the following purposes:
To provide and improve the App and its features
To personalize your experience with the App
To analyze how the App is used
To communicate with you, such as sending you updates or promotional offers (with your consent)
To comply with legal and regulatory requirements
Sharing Your Information
We may share your information with third-party service providers who help us operate the App. These service providers are contractually obligated to keep your information confidential and secure. We will not share your information with any other third party without your consent, except as required by law.
Your Choices
You have choices regarding your information:​
You can opt out of receiving marketing communications from us by following the unsubscribe instructions in those communications.
You can disable cookies through your device settings. However, this may limit your ability to use certain features of the App.
Data Security
We take reasonable steps to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no internet or electronic storage system is 100% secure.
​
Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on the App.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
hello@littlelove.app
